 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search AI Designer inXile entertainment 2 reviews Tustin, CA Full-time inXile entertainment 2 reviews Read what people are saying about working here. Job details Job Type Full-time Full Job Description Do you sit and watch the patterns of enemies in every game you play? Do you watch the citizens in a town of your favorite RPG go about their daily routines? Do you have the knowledge and design experience to work with a group of multi-disciplined developers to create best in class AI experiences? If so, then inXile has an amazing opportunity for you. 
 
 We are searching the globe for our next hyper-creative AI Designer to work on our unannounced, next-gen project. You will collaborate and take direction from the Lead Combat Designer and Game Director to work with a multi-discipline team, designing and implementing exhilarating AI experiences.
 Currently, given these unprecedented times, positions at inXile are offered as a virtual/remote workplace. 
 
 Responsibilities 
 
 Collaborate with Design Leads to own and implement the vision for AI 
 Design and implement enemy characters, including boss encounters, with unique behaviors 
 Design and implement ambient AI characters, including town inhabitants, shop keepers and mission NPCs 
 Work closely with animators to implement, tune, and adjust timing of enemy moves/abilities 
 Work closely with animators to maintain a cutting-edge level of fidelity with all AI characters 
 Collaborate with animation, art, audio, and visual effects to ensure AI behaviors are readable to players 
 Work with the Combat Player team to make enemies take advantage of status effects, resistances, damage interactions, and unique enemy reaction states 
 Selflessly design experiences with accessibility in mind 
 Be an advocate for the player 
 
 
Required Skills 
 
 Designed, prototyped, and implemented AI characters 
 Can break down and explain game mechanics 
 Understand the moment-to-moment gameplay loops of first-person shooters and RPGs and what makes those genres fun 
